COMPILING FEEL++ ON TITANE
--------------------------

Adapted from curie's scripts

Tested with Feel++/mortar_m2an/r49c501572531
on Fri, Dec 14, 2012

Minimal requirements
 - g++    >=4.4  (tested with 4.6.3)
 - lapack        (tested with 3.4.1)
 - petsc  >=3.1  (tested with 3.3)
 - boost  >=1.46 (tested with 1.49)
 - gmsh          (tested with 2.6.1)

Use $CCCWORKDIR for local libraries
Use $SCRATCHDIR for build files
